      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ADHANA MARTINA (7) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fourth (26.12) last time in a Grade 6 at Murray Bridge. Has a good record here including four wins. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from four starts. Tough to beat if on-song. JUST A NUISANCE (3) had the drop on the lead from the inside before drawing clear to score (30.87) at this track in a Grade 5/6 over 530m. Yet to score from this box but has never missed the frame in two starts. Leading chance again. COOL BLUE YOU (1) wasn't far away at the finish when 5th and beaten only 2.75 lengths (30.89) at this track. Yet to miss the placings from four starts out of this box. Can do much better this time. KICKER DUSTY (5) is new to this trip but not to be underestimated.",
